leads.lead_text: Corolla usually zygomorphic, variously coloured, rarely white; stamens enclosed or exserted, aggregated together or distally convergent; fruit dry, or rarely, succulent
Corolla actinomorphic or nearly so, white or rarely pinkish; stamens usually exserted with distal ends parallel or diverging; fruit succulent, or rarely, dry
